9 graham crackers
3 T Sugar
1/2 t ground ginger
1/2 t cinnamon
1/2 t ground cloves
6 T unsalted butter

Blend the graham crackers, sugar, ginger, cinnamon and cloves in a blender using 15 - 2 second pulses

Melt the butter and fold it into the mixture.

Using a 9 in pan, press the graham cracker mixture down to the bottom using a cup. Then use a spoon to push the graham cracker mixture into the side.

Bake the crust in the oven at 325 for 15 minutes.